para_trans: Regarding sanctioning and disbursement of grants-in-aid to Maharashtra Coastal Zone Management Authority.
Department of Environment and Climate Change
Government Correctional Certificate No: MCZMA 2024 / Q. No.5 / T / C-4
Madam Cama Road, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Read: - 1) Government Decision No: MCZMA 2024 / Q. No.5 / TAC-4, D. March 13, 2024.
Paragraph No. 1 of the Government Decision in respect of the above. The serial number in 2 is the text in 4.
The following text is being added next.

The Maharashtra Coastal Management Authority (MCZMA) has been allotted Rs. A sum of ₹35 million is being disbursed through the present Government decision. Subsidies granted accordingly are non-refundable. Accordingly, the funds disbursed are being disbursed with the condition that the next instalment of funds is disbursed after submitting the utilization certificate to the Department.
This government certificate is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
